  m_Name: FarmerNode2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  _lines:
  - I'm old and can no longer perform such labor. I need you to gather 5 apples and
    5 honey from the forest around this cabin.
  npc: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6165f3d3174910c499db7a1126ae0d83, type: 2}
  _playerReplyOptions:
  - 'Ok! I will go gather apples and honey from this forest, and return once I have
    5 of each! '
  - No, I need some time to prepare.
